title: Should we spend $102K for the PBOY 1 of 1?
body:
NFT: https://opensea.io/assets/0x495f947276749ce646f68ac8c248420045cb7b5e/12196644238781453939224022727715170486060734546117498519503808060481588953089

Pascal Boyart (PBOY) is one of the most famous street artists working on NFTs. His work is rebellious and Pascal fights for censorship resistance. Just like the rest of us in crypto! 

This piece is called The Creation of Adam, interpreted from the Sistine Chapel. It was painted in a semi-squat house in a building that was previously a gold foundry. There is a documentary that follows the creation of this masterpiece (subtitles available on youtube preferences): https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fsRFHmdiyGE
